wf.a.LabelAction.displayName: Update YAML Manifests in CD repo

entry.string: rm -rf Multi-Tier-BankApp-CD git clone https://github.com/SRUSHTI-AGARWAL/Multi-Tier-BankApp-CD.git cd Multi-Tier-BankApp-CD ls -l bankapp repo_dir=$(pwd) sed -i 's|image: imsrushti/bankapp:.*|image: imsrushti/bankapp:'"${DOCKER_TAG}"'|' ${repo_dir}/bankapp/bankapp-ds.yml
cd Multi-Tier-BankApp-CD git config user.email "ssd125agarwal@gmail.com" git config user.name "SRUSHTI-AGARWAL"
cd Multi-Tier-BankApp-CD ls git add bankapp/bankapp-ds.yml git commit -m "Update images to ${DOCKER_TAG}" git push origin main
